Police in King Williams Town on Thursday arrested two suspects, aged between 25 and 30 years old, for robbery with a knife in the King Williams Town CBD.According to the police, the victim was robbed of his cellphone and he immediately stopped police that were patrolling along Oak Street, King Williams Town. Police gave chase and managed to arrest these suspects and recovered the cellphone, said police spokesperson, Captain Siphokazi Mawisa.She added that it was handed over to the victim.The suspects will appear at court soon.